section.def:
Commissioner
                (差餉物業估價署署長) means the Commissioner of Rating and
            Valuation;

paragraph.content:
to be for the same term as is specified in the proviso for renewal in the
                renewable Government lease of the lot or section to which the new Government lease
                relates;

to commence immediately on the expiration of the term of the renewable
                Government lease of the lot or section to which the new Government lease
                relates;

a covenant by the lessee to pay the new Government rent in the same manner and
                on the same days as are specified in the renewable Government lease of the lot or
                section to which the new Government lease relates;

in the case of a lot, cause the plan to be annexed to the counterpart of the
                renewable Government lease of the lot kept in the Land Registry and cause the
                previous plan, if any, to be cancelled;
